# Short dictionary of how the dynasties are split into kingdoms:
# - Mumakan
# - Koronade
# - Mulambur
# - Mulakan
# - Hathor
# - Tuktan
# - Dushera

###           ###
###  Mumakan  ###
###           ###
#################

### Semi-Mythical Creation ###

lineofamav1 = {
    name = amav
    dna = amav_dna

    dynasty = dynasty_amav
    religion = faith_amav
    culture = akanali

    trait = just
    trait = compassionate
    trait = lustful

    diplomacy = 10
    martial = 7
    stewardship = 6
    intrigue = 8
    learning = 10
    prowess = 12

    trait = education_learning_5
    trait = beauty_good_3
    trait = saint
    trait = lifestyle_mystic
    trait = paragon

    284.10.14 = {
        birth = yes
    }

    385.8.18 = {
        death = {
            death_reason = death_disappearance
        }
    }
}

### Third Restoration ###
### Emperors of Mumakan
# Established by Ji Indur after his second return in the 2500s, rule until the War of the Ring, though not without instability and house jumping
